{"tid":1575021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報：台灣或落到零邦交境地","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T18:01:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a2980361d639acf74cb396266839decae7581dc6","tid":1575021,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"南太平洋島國所羅門政府內閣開會後決定與台北斷交，轉而與北京建交，台北政府晚上宣布，即時與所羅門群島斷交，今次是總統蔡英文上台3年多來，第6個與台北斷交的國家，台灣的邦交國剩餘16個。<br />\n<br />\n北京環球時報發表社評，指蔡英文當局在所羅門群島宣布斷交的第一時間，指責中國大陸搞&ldquo;金錢外交&rdquo;，是賊喊捉賊，靠金錢來維繫不正當對外&ldquo;邦交關係&rdquo;的是台灣當局，指台灣還將繼續失去&ldquo;邦交國&rdquo;，直至可能落到&ldquo;零邦交&rdquo;的境地，美國對台北當局的支持，恐怕亦難改變這個趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n原因是中國已經強大，在世界經濟和政治都已舉足輕重，任何一個正常國家都沒有理由站到北京的對立面，大多數小國拋棄台灣與北京建交成為長期戰略選擇。"},{"pid":"38c99c9c78d52638ca3adfb998f938f3138ea440","tid":1575021,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172510&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1172510%26csid%3D261_341&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=51d534ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172510&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0887696dd62838c170710f1ef0385ed0bf3eb9f0","tid":1575021,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"568fced717c25af033cfd794c76a74c3bb3198a8","tid":1575021,"uid":53666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"同香港建交啦"},{"pid":"46540699232103fff131653cee5f9066f7b2cbc1","tid":1575021,"uid":45975,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"但人地去美國免簽證"},{"pid":"4ce3d093180999f89fb72525e3b15e1a217d8f6b","tid":1575021,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46540699232103fff131653ce